summary: Removes the goat trophy/wall mount in Honeyside.
descriptionHtml:
Honeyside's probably my favorite house in the game but the goat trophy on the wall kind of ruins it for me. I got tired of deleting it with every new game so I did it with the creation kit. Enjoy! :)
<br />
<br />Install:
<br />Extract into Data folder
<br />
<br />or use a mod manager such as NMM, MO, etc
author: gyashaa
